.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, paramedic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, trance
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, water-polo
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the pilot##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Job         | pilot    | paramedic    |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | metal      |
| Sport         | basketball | water-polo |

