The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |
