.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, coral
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, superhero
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, ship
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Color           | coral     | white |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy  |
| Transport     | ship      | boat |

